sent.orig: Assemble disc screw through disc washer and disc rubber, and screw it into disc holder.
sent.trans: 穿过阀瓣垫圈和阀瓣橡胶组装阀瓣螺丝，并将其旋进阀瓣固定器内。

sent.orig: Assemble disc screw through disc washer and rubber and screw into disc holder.
sent.trans: 将阀瓣螺丝穿过阀瓣垫圈和橡胶，安装到阀瓣固定器上。

sent.orig: Note: disc rubber is molded into disc holder and is supplied as a disc holder assembly.
sent.trans: 注意：阀瓣橡胶是模制到阀瓣固定器上的，并作为阀瓣固定器总成一起提供。

sent.orig: CD-V (compact disc with video) is the laser disc with videos.
Disc hanger is supported on a sturdy disc carrier hinge pin of excellent bearing qualities.
sent.trans: 阀瓣支架由坚固的、具有高级轴承品质的阀瓣支架铰链销支撑。
